<h1>npm forever</h1>

<p>2014-01-31 03:59 Friday</p>

<p><a href="https://npmjs.org/package/forever" target="_blank">https://npmjs.org/package/forever</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/nodejitsu/forever" target="_blank">https://github.com/nodejitsu/forever</a></p>

<p>A simple CLI tool for ensuring that a given node script runs continuously (i.e. forever)</p>

<pre>
npm install forever</pre>

